{"tid":2086294,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"拒絕恐懼，連登公投，聽日71你出唔出去行街 (認真答)","createTime":"2020-06-30T08:39:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-01T13:53:02.000Z","uid":94771,"like":150,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"9929b1351359b8f7e91381563fea962d3d0b56d9","tid":2086294,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T08:39:42.000Z","msg":"我明眾志解散，學生動源，民族陣線解散香港總部，龍門退出所謂佢口中的＂黃圈＂會令到大家好恐懼<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>由有小部份連登仔要求刪帳號，刪POST就可以睇得出恐懼已經傳播緊，我都睇得出FaceBook同Twitter都好大機會有同樣時情發生緊</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n所以係依個時候，我再想問大家，浪費佐成個星期時間宣傳的71，大量人響應的71遊行，你地會點做<br />\n<br />\n戰勝恐懼，所以聽日照出去　<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n開頭以為支那得個講唔過，依家會過，我好淆，所以聽日會唔出　<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/COXt8HK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCOXt8HK.jpg&h=ec8e9287&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JRKsEPq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJRKsEPq.jpg&h=e3ec2018&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xXOkZPq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxXOkZPq.jpg&h=529d02b3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"756246abb351262871e7ca3840a8a78d5dcbce36","tid":2086294,"uid":235501,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T08:40:55.000Z","msg":"推 唔好比放負散水撚帶到風向"},{"pid":"63cd647c7db9d1f834ad98d91329cf7c49959e8d","tid":2086294,"uid":38563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T08:41:27.000Z","msg":"出<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85f3e6edca3a7f5604f08944835994cf5967cf36","tid":2086294,"uid":4931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T08:41:33.000Z","msg":"出，連街都唔敢出就太可憐"},{"pid":"6e695904f5679450d7b201e850039b41bad12e6b","tid":2086294,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score